I started watching a few weeks before you decided to shift away from lolita. I had just dropped out of highschool because my depression was completely debilitating. I couldn't get out of bed. I never spoke to anyone. Your videos were (and still are) such a fucking ray of sunshine in a really dark time in my life. Since then you've been through different styles and jobs, a network, a band! You graduated, got into your dream school and your channel is finally getting the following it deserves! I know a lot of people say how much you inspire them but I want you to know that I've also come a long way! I got my diploma, which I never imagined I could accomplish, I got a job, moved to Chicago, made friends.  I hope that we can both continue to grow! I'm so so proud!!
